2018-09-13 Version 59.0 (24)
 * App now supports the new version string format (from two to three digits)
 * Show only update notification when a new update is available (caused by misinterpreted version strings)

2018-07-24 Version 58.0 (23)
 * support for Firefox Beta, Firefox Nightly, Firefox Focus, Firefox Klar
 * checks in background every 4 hours for updates + display notification when updates are available

